<h1>Donating to Snowdrift.coop
<h2>The crowdmatch pledge
<p>
  Our crowdmatching system is in live testing, so you can #
  <a href=@{SnowdriftProjectR}>pledge within the system itself!
  To have more impact there, invite others to join the crowd.
<h2>Volunteering
<p>
  Aside from money, you can donate time by <a href="https://wiki.snowdrift.coop/community/how-to-help">volunteering</a>.
<h2>Direct donations
<p>
  During our beta testing / startup phase, we welcome larger donations and grants.

<hr>
