<h3>Tax-deductible donations under 501(c)(3)
<p>
  Snowdrift.coop is incorporated as a Michigan non-profit cooperative but does
  not have independent federal tax-exempt status.
  We have in the past gotten grants from 501(c)(3) organizations, and that may
  be possible again. If you are looking to donate that way, please #
  <a href=@{ContactR}>contact&nbsp;us
  so that we can discuss the options.

<hr>

<h3> Thank you for your support!

<ul>
  <li> We honor donors in our public list of <a href=@{SponsorsR}>launch sponsors</a>
  <li> at $12+, we can send a physical <a href=@{MerchandiseR}#stickers>sticker</a> upon request
  <li> $40+ donors may sponsor a specific commit change in our code
  <li> donate $100+ for a <a href=@{MerchandiseR}#t-shirts>t-shirt</a> (supply limited currently, future printings not planned yet)
  <li> $500+ grants are distinguished as "key sponsors".
